      "body": "<p>This should cover you:</p>\n<pre><code>String lines[] = string.split(&quot;\\\\r?\\\\n&quot;);\n</code></pre>\n<p>There are only really two newlines (UNIX and Windows) that you need to worry about, and this Regex covers both cases.</p>\n"
